node.text:
After completing my foundation and concealer i set with two different powders, one being the shade Banana (all over) to lock in my foundation then Vanilla to bake. 
This powder formula provides a long wearing Matte finish for up to  24 hours. They are also water, smudge and sweat proof meaning they won’t budge 👏🏼. They are available in 6 shades @sephora.

#iluvsarahii #ad

use my code ILUVSARAHII on their:

"El Pari Pack", includes all 7 flavors in 5oz and 4 gummies. Regular Price $50.00 with the discount total its $42.50(free shipping)

2 cups of Frozen Mango

node.text: I have been itching to do a double graphic liner and this is the perfect product to achieve the look. It may look hard but the rich cushiony formula glides right on making it easy to build and blend out. This cream eyeshadow is infused with primer so it lasts for 24hours leaving a matte finish that won’t transfer, fade, smudge or sweat off. It’s also a multi-use product that you can use even on your brows and cheeks! #SmashboxPartner #AlwaysOnSmashbox

node.title: Getting creative with @smashboxcosmetics Always On Cream Shadows 🎨

node.text:
who else is loving this look?! It’s so easy to recreate and today I want to teach you guys how to achieve it using my Sweet Oasis Palette from @morphebrushes. 
I love how versatile this Palette is, I can create a bold bright eye or a neutral look like this with a pop of blue ! Let me know what you guys think. The Palette goes live on ULTA 2/14 & available on Morphe.com (use code iluvsarahii)

#iluvsarahii #morphepartner #morphesweetoasis

node.title: Neutral eye with a pop of blue🔥

node.text:
My fingers say we’re this close to spooky season but I’m already getting into the vampy looks🤩🍁🍂
_____________________________________
Tutorial for this look is saved in my Makeup Highlights 

Brows | @benefitcosmetics Powmade 4.5 
Eyes | @colourpopcosmetics It’s a mood palette 
Face | @milkmakeup Grip Primer + @narsissist Natural Radiance Foundation in Stromboli 
Concealer | @anastasiabeverlyhills Magic Touch Concealer in 9 
Powder | @makeupforever HD matte setting powder in banana 2.0 + vanilla 1.0
Cheeks | @kvdbeauty Peony Blush 
Lips | @maccosmetics Cork Lip pencil + @doseofcolors Liquid Lip in Supernatural

node.text:
After completing my foundation and concealer i set with two different powders, one being the shade Banana (all over) to lock in my foundation then Vanilla to bake. 
This powder formula provides a long wearing Matte finish for up to  24 hours. They are also water, smudge and sweat proof meaning they won’t budge 👏🏼. They are available in 6 shades @sephora.

node.text:
It’s time to bring back lip videos so today I’m sharing my current go to  nude lip combo👏🏼 This combo goes perfect with any makeup day or night.

First step: 
Set your lips with powder, yes powder and all l over . Im using @ctilburymakeup Airbursh Flawless powder 

Next line lips: i always pair 2 lip pencils, my favorite/must haves are @maccosmetics Stripdown and Cork . I like with stripdown first all over and then move in with cork to add more color/contrast but  I was out of so used @vievemuse Bark.

Lastly: Add @nyxcosmetics Soft Matte Cream in London. This color is stunning and formula is stunning + it’s affordable! 

Tada! Xo ✨#iluvsarahii #nudelip

I got the magic touch ✨🪄 #ad
The new @anastasiabeverlyhills magic touch concealer is everything!!!!! First, it’s a multi-use concealer so you can use it more than just underneath your eyes. I like to use it as a shadow base and under my brow bone to highlight. It has a beautiful natural second skin finish with a medium-to-full coverage that ✨magically✨brightens, corrects and blurs. I’m using shade 9.

#ABHMagicTouch #iluvsarahii

My favorite part of the day is taking off my makeup and if there’s one step that makes the process faster, easier and efficient it’s breaking my makeup down with a cleansing balm. This Green Clean makeup cleansing balm from @farmacybeauty has been my recent obsession. It melts everything off even the most long wearing face, lips and eye products leaving ZERO residue. 
It even has active ingredients such as sunflower + Ginger Root Oil, Turmeric, Moringa Extract and Papaya Enzymes all which renew your skin leaving it soft and silky and ready for your nighttime skincare routine. 

#iluvsarahii #FarmacyBeauty #ad
